description:
Design and implement improvements at the existing play facility owned and managed by Worcester City Council. The required outcomes will be:
• Bespoke, inspiring, neighbourhood play space that fits in its surroundings
and enhances the local environment;
• To meet the needs of the local community by creating an inclusive space
for all;
• To support the Council aims as part of the Worcester Play Plan

